lead_paragraph: “The Hunting Ground,” which was shown in full on CNN despite a threat of legal action from a lawyer for Jameis Winston, had an average of 179,000 live and same-day viewers in the 25-to-54 age group.

headline.main: Documentary About Rape at Colleges Draws Viewers in Key Demographic
